# aws-config-loader-286349

AWS configuration utilities for Python applications.

## Installation

```bash
pip install aws-config-loader-286349
```

## Usage

```python
from aws_config_loader_286349 import get_config, get_client

# Get AWS configuration
config = get_config()

# Get S3 client
s3 = get_client('s3')
```
